{"id": "art-253", "label": "Art. 253", "title": "Art. 253", "slug": "art-253", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 253 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Lichidatorii\nvor putea fi persoane fizice sau persoane juridice. Lichidatorii persoane\nfizice sau <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>permanen&#355;i</span>\n- persoane fizice ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nlichidatoare - trebuie s&#259; fie lichidatori <span class=SpellE>autoriza&#355;i</span>,\nîn <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legii</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1458005724\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1167\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1458005724\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Lichidatorii au <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span>\nr&#259;spundere ca <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> administratorii, respectiv\nmembrii directoratului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_553214472\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1166\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_553214472\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Lichidatorii sunt datori, îndat&#259; dup&#259;\npreluarea <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iei</span>, ca împreun&#259; cu\ndirectorii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> administratorii, respectiv cu\nmembrii directoratului <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, s&#259;\nfac&#259; un inventar <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; încheie un <span\nclass=SpellE>bilan&#355;</span>, care s&#259; constate <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nexact&#259; a activului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivului <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; le semneze.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_693353161\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1165\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_693353161\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Lichidatorii sunt <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;i</span>\ns&#259; primeasc&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; p&#259;streze\npatrimoniul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, registrele ce li\ns-au <span class=SpellE>încredin&#355;at</span> de administratori, respectiv de\nmembrii directoratului, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> actele <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. De asemenea, <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nvor <span class=SpellE>&#355;ine</span> un registru cu toate <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iunile</span> lichid&#259;rii, în ordinea datei lor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2098261298\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1164\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2098261298\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Lichidatorii <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nîndeplinesc mandatul sub controlul cenzorilor. În cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> organizate potrivit sistemului\ndualist, lichidatorii <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> îndeplinesc mandatul\nsub controlul consiliului de supraveghere.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}